Name: Ultra Mission™
About the game: The date: January 12, 2081 The location: Otto Labs headquarters The objective: Find out what the heck is going on! Embark on a dangerous investigation in Ultra Mission™ , the latest arcade-inspired shooter from Gumbo Machine™. As an agent of the Stellar Exchange Commission , you must traverse the labyrinthine maze that is Otto Labs . Each of Ultra Mission's 20 levels is littered with powerful automatons and questionable experiments. One thing is certain: this is going to be a blast!
